Distribution in Paratethys.
Badenian (middle Miocene): 
Eisenstadt-Sopron Basin:
Forchtenau (
Hoernes & Auinger 1879
); 
Pannonian Basin:
Borsodbóta, Diósd, Letkés, Szob, 
Budapest
: Illés street, Örs vezér square (
Hungary
) (
Kovács & Vicián 2013
); 
Transylvanian Basin:
Lăpugiu de Sus, Coşteiu de Sus (
Romania
) (
Hoernes & Auinger 1879
). The occurrence of this species in the Tortonian of Barcelona, mentioned by Faura I Sans (1908), needs confirmation.
